Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:54.83,Default,Ijima,0,0,0,,{I'll protect Isana.} Ochráním Isanu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:58.05,Default,Ijima,0,0,0,,{And Engi, and Kounagi, too.} A Engi a taky Kounagi.
