Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:04.36,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,{Fujiwara.} Fujiwara-san
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:09.60,Default,Play,0,0,0,,{I see. So that's your...} Aha. Tak tohle je tvůj...
