Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:37.38,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{All of the things I've felt here will turn into my strength.} Všechny věci, které jsem cítil se zde promění v mojí sílu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:42.88,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{Strength in a Dream... Strength in a Dream is...} Síla ve snu... Síla ve snu je...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.68,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{You human.} Ten člověk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.39,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{The strength of will!} Síla mé vůle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:59.15,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{I'll be borrowing this for a bit, John.} Nachvíli si to půjčím, Johne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:02.99,Default,Play,0,0,0,,{What in the...} Co to je...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:10.58,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{It won't go the way it did earlier.} Už ti to nebude procházet, jako předtím.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:14.16,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{I hope you'll let me have some fun.} Doufám, že mi dovolíš se bavit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.92,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{Nothing can break this sword.} Nic nemůže zlomit tenhle meč.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:25.68,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{Not if I believe in it with all my heart.} Ne, když tomu věřím celým svým srdcem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:27.09,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{What's going on?} Co se děje?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.69,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{Those are some half-hearted attacks.} To jsou nějaký váhavý útoky.{meta here: changed half-hearted to half-assed just because "heart" was mentioned earlier too many times}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:50.03,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{Nice try, human.} Dobrej pokus, člověku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.03,0:13:55.08,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{Getting cut by Engi hurt a hundred times worse.} Schytat seknutí od Engi bolí stokrát víc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:56.21,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{I'm putting an end to this.} Skončím to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:59.25,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,{No!}Ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:07.26,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{My dream is to never give up.} Můj sen je se nikdy nevzdat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:08.76,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{And to protect everyone.} A všechny ochránit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:12.43,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{And to send Merry back to her world.} A poslat Merry zpátky do jejího světa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:17.31,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{What are you talking about, human?} O čem to mluvíš, člověku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:32.16,Default,Play,0,0,0,,Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:41.79,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{What's with this human?} Co je s tímhle člověkem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:42.63,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{Creepy.} Děsivý.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:48.72,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{I won't stop. I won't give up.} Nezastavím se. Nevzdám se.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:00.35,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{That one hurt.} Tohle bolelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:03.54,Default,Ijima,0,0,0,,{Is he really human?} Je vážně člověk?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:10.32,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,{Merry, please wake up! At this rate Fujiwara's going to...} Merry prosím vzbuď se! V tomhle tempu Fujiwara...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:12.28,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:22.63,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,{People from the brass band club have guts, you know!} Lidi hudebky mají taky kuráž, víš!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:31.38,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{I won't give up. I'll send Merry back to her world.} Nevzdám se. Pošlu Merry zpátky do jejího světa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:38.31,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,{Merry, please wake up! Fujiwara is...} Merry, prosím vzbuď se! Fujiwara je...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry-san. {missing line}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:54.16,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{Yumeji said he'd send me back to my world.} Yumeji řekl, že mě pošle zpátky do mého světa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:56.95,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{He said he believes in me.} Řekl, že mi věří.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:59.75,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{I won't forgive anyone} Neodpustím tomu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:01.75,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{who hurts Yumeji! } kdo ublíží Yumejimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:25.02,Default,Play,0,0,0,,{You said that strength in a Dream is the strength of will, did you not, Yumeji?} Řekl si, že síla ve snu je síla tvé vůle, neřekl, Yumeji-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:34.16,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,{Engi! Your world is back!} Engi! Tvůj svět je zpátky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:44.17,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{My forest disappeared.} Můj les zmizel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:46.33,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{Don't get distracted!} Nenech se rozptýlit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.22,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{Forest-woman!} Lesní ženo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.60,Default,Play,0,0,0,,{Violet Flash in the Moonlight, Sannasubi.} Fialový záblesk měsíce, Sannasubi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:11.32,Default,Play,0,0,0,,{Oh, no!} To, ne!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.70,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{What was that, Forest-woman?} Co to bylo, lesní ženo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.00,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{What did you just do?} Co si udělala?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:29.13,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{So, can you defeat me now?} Takže, teď už mě můžeš porazit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:33.71,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{Can you tear me apart knowing you'd destroy her dream in the process?} Můžeš mě zabít, i když víš, že by to mohlo zničit její sny?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:35.80,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{Well?} Takže?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:15.84,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{Jeez, this is turning into a situation with no hope or dreams.}{meta here: stupid, stupid, stupid catch phrase.}Bože, tohle se obrací do situace bez naděje a snů.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.43,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{Don't give up, Merry.} Nevzdávej se, Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:24.35,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{It doesn't matter that she's captured Parade.} Nezáleží na tom, jestli zajala Palletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:26.23,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{Send him back to the Dream World.}Pošli ho zpátky do světa snů.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:31.65,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{You can do it.}Ty to zvládneš.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:34.32,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{I believe in you.} Věřím ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:37.28,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{Believe in yourself. }Merry, věř v sebe.{meta here: don't believe in yourself, believe in me who believes in you}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:43.53,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{All right.} Dobře.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:48.08,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{Can you really kill me?} Vážně mě můžeš zabít?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:49.54,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{You're softies for dreams.} Jste měkoty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.46,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{Why don't you just die instead?} Proč prostě neumřete?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.34,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{I believe in Yumeji.} Veřím v Yumejiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:57.92,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{I believe in myself.} Věřím v sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:04.35,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{I'll send Parade back!} Pošlu Palletta zpátky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:14.69,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,{That's the mark from Leon's gun.} To je znak z Leonovo zbraně.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:26.62,Default,Parade,0,0,0,,{Thank you!} Děkuju!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:31.54,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{Parade.}Pallette.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.25,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{Isana.}Isano.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:39.55,Default,Tree,0,0,0,,{What are you? What the hell are you?} Co jsi? Co jsi sakra zač?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:45.18,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{I still haven't introduced myself.} Ještě jsem se nepředstavila.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:47.72,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{I gobble up bad Dream Demons.} Pohlcuji zlé démony snů.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:52.52,Default,Merry,0,0,0,, {I'm Dreameater Merry!} Jsem Pojídačka snů Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:56.69,Default,Play,0,0,0,,{You're finished!} Skončila si!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.99,Default,Isana,0,0,0,,{Huh? What happened to Mr. Ijima?} Huh? Kde je pan učitel Ijima?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:11.27,Default,Isana,0,0,0,,{He was here wasn't he? He was...} Byl tady ne? Byl...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:14.83,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{Really? Are you sure about that?} Opravdu? Jsi si tím jistá?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.00,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{Maybe he left.}Možná odešel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:20.05,Default,Isana,0,0,0,,{But, I'm pretty sure that just until a moment ago he...}Ale jsem si docela jistá, že před chvílí...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:24.72,Default,Isana,0,0,0,,{Dad, forget about that extra-large curry order! Mr. Ijima left.} Tati, zapomeň na tu objednávku! Pan učitel Ijima odešel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:29.43,Default,Yui,0,0,0,,{Kawanami, Tachibana is the same as always.} Kawinami-san, Tachibana-san je stejná jako vždy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:37.40,Default,Saki,0,0,0,,{I was really surprised that Mr. Ijima quit all of a sudden.} Vážně jsem byla překvapená, že pan učitel Ijima skončil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:39.07,Default,Saki,0,0,0,,{He was such a good teacher.}Byl to dobrý učitel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:43.57,Default,Taka,0,0,0,,{The homeroom teacher, the counselor, both vanish at once.} Třídní učitel, poradce, oba zmizeli najednou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:46.03,Default,Taka,0,0,0,,{By Akiyanagi Takateru.}Od Akiyanagi Takateru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:51.41,Default,Saki,0,0,0,,{He was the one who made Sana realize her dream.} On byl ten, díky kterému si Sana uvědomila svůj sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.91,Default,Saki,0,0,0,,{I think she wanted to express her gratitude to him properly.} Myslím si, že mu chtěla poděkovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:58.71,Default,Taka,0,0,0,,{So what's your dream?} Takže, co je tvůj sen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:04.05,Default,Saki,0,0,0,,{Woah, Taka! Don't be so serious all of a sudden.} Woah, Tako! Nebuď tak vážný najednou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:04.57,Default,Saki,0,0,0,,{Let's get going.} Pojď.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:07.55,Default,Saki,0,0,0,,{There's no way I could tell you.} Neni šance, že bych ti to řekla.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:10.72,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{It's finally over.} Konečně je po všem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:14.64,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{I guess.}Asi jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:17.08,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{But there's still something important left to be done.} Ale pořád ještě něco zbývá dořešit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:19.82,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{I've got to send you back.} Musím tě poslat zpátky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:23.19,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{That's right! That was our contract.} To je pravda! To je naše dohoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:25.99,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{Sure, a contract is a contract.} Jasně, dohoda je dohoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:26.70,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{Yup.}Jop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:30.91,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{I wonder what will happen to Chizuru.}Zajímalo by mě co se stane s Chizuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:34.46,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{Will she stay that way forever?} Bude taková navždy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:38.92,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{She doesn't remember Isana or any of us.} Nepamatuje si Isanu ani nikoho z nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:43.46,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{That's because her soul and dreams were both shattered.} To je, protože její duše a sny byly rozbity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:50.93,Default,Isana,0,0,0,,{ What's this? You're not getting it black today?} Co to? Dneska si nedáš černou?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.73,0:21:58.94,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{But I'm sure she can start all over again.} Ale jsem si jistý, že to zvládne znovu{od začátku}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:06.40,Default,Yumeji,0,0,0,,{Because there's no limit on the number of dreams a person can have.} Protože tu není limit toho, kolik může mít člověk snů.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.07,0:22:08.86,Default,Merry,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Hm.
